title: A discussion on Sun Tzu's book The Art Of War
itunes:title: A discussion on Sun Tzu's book The Art Of War
description:
George Noory and Gary Gagliardi, discuss Sun Tzu’s The Art of War, Gary sheds light on the ancient Chinese philosopher's principles of "winning without conflict" and how these ideas can apply to peoples' personal lives.
